snippet: Trajal Harrell presents in full his seven-part “Twenty Looks or Paris Is Burning at the Judson Church” at the Kitchen.
abstract: Siobhan Burke reviews national premiere of seven-part dance piece Twenty Looks or Paris Is Burning at the Judson Church, choreographed and performed by Trajal Harrell, at The Kitchen as part of Crossing the Line festival.
lead_paragraph: Trajal Harrell presents in full his seven-part “Twenty Looks or Paris Is Burning at the Judson Church” at the Kitchen.
